creator: Olives
descriptionHtml:
Try to be the owner of all the shopping mall minimart here, unlock all decks of grocery items and you can finally become the world-famous business tycoon! Sell organic goods in your market minimart. Keep customers happy and earn money to unlock decks all over the place. Supermarket minimart is a fun supermarket management game where you start by managing your small markets and slowly turn into a beautiful supermall minimart. Run a grocery store and accept big amounts of organic supplies from your own farms.

Manage and try to expand supermarket mini mart. As long as you hold enough money, new shopping malls and more customers will be served!

Be your own boss, run a mini mart supermarket, and enjoy the relaxing journey of selling products for fun. Hire the employees to help you build your mini mart supermarket and expand your business. Start from a small mini-mart and grow it to a business empire. Serve customers, earn money, hire workers and become the biggest tycoon of shopping malls in town!
Earn money to unlock different fruits and vegetable marts. You can upgrade marts to increase their capacity to store and entertain customers. Mini mart: supermarket is a fun product selling simulation based on real-life business ideas.
Start form tomatoes and earn money to open the next store in your supermarket minimart to entertain maximum customers. Grow your business ideas by hiring employees for your mini mart. This supermarket minimart has a lot of sections open them all to provide best shopping services to your customers. Upgrade your racks and bases to entertain a maximum number of customers at a time in supermarket minimart. Delivery trucks are important in any mini mart so upgrade them from time to time to achieve maximum products in your minimart in time. Build and extend your supermarket minimart. Serve customers, earn money, hire workers and become the biggest shopping mall minimart owner in town!

Earn money, unlock and upgrades all racks to and make your supermarket more attractive by placing different customer support items in your minimart. At the Minimart supermarket, customers are lining up to buy grocery items according to their list. Send them with required items with smile and upgrade your minimart to make sure crowd is coming.

Features:
• Fun and easy to play
• Beautiful graphics and friendly UI
• Attractive animations and sound effects
• Soothing sound effects
• Upgrades are available for every items and employees

How to play:
• Simple one-touch control
• Simple and user friendly UI
• Easy upgrades
